SubjectOrder Authorizing the Minister of Veterans Affairs to Verify Previous Service to Confirm Veteran Homelessness Program Eligibility
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Veterans Affairs to verify previous service in either the Canadian Armed Forces or the Royal Canadian Mounted Police in order to confirm eligibility of participants in the VETERAN HOMELESSNESS PROGRAM.
